messages.content: Hi, thank you for calling Vacation Village Resorts. Our offices are currently closed. This is Jamie, a virtual agent on a recorded line. How can I help you today?
I'm trying to get into my account. The account number is wrong. My name is Caitlin Luker. K a t e l y n. L u k e r.
Let me check your account details. Can you confirm your date of birth? Alright Caitlin, can you share the phone number you have on your contract?
Eight one three five nine nine seven six six one.
Just a sec while I pull up your account.
Alright, I was able to pull up a record using your phone number. Can you please confirm the spelling of your first and last name one more time?
K a t e l y n l u k e r.
Thanks for confirming. Can you tell me your state of residence?
Florida,
Great, I have you verified. Go ahead and let me know what you need help
with today.
My account number is invalid.
I see your concern about the account number. Can you tell me what happens when you try to log in?
Tells me this is not a valid ID. This is an invalid account number.
Got it, you're getting an invalid account number error when trying to log in. Would you like to receive a new registration link for Clubhouse
to set up your account?
No. I've we
just did this. You sent me it already and it did not work.
Understood, so the registration link did not work for you. Are you trying to access your ownership information or make a payment?
Correct.
Make a payment.
Alright, you’d like to make a payment. Just to confirm, is this for your Vacation Village at Parkway property, contract number
three one one zero zero six three?
Yes.
The email I have on file is katieluker1@gmail.com and the phone number is eight one three
-- five nine nine -- seven six six one. Are these correct?
Yes. That's correct.
Alright, working on your payment link now.
Is there anything else you need help with today?
No.
Alright, you’ll receive a payment link shortly by email and text. Have a great day.
